author: Graeme Campbell
title: Patta Drops a Collection of Burgundy Luggage Bangers for SS17
text:
Visit the original post to see all 2 images from this gallery. 
We’ve already had a look at Patta’s sartorial offerings for SS17, and now the Dutch streetwear brand compliments the range with an additional luggage haul.
The collection is inspired by a burgundy color theme and comprises an adjustable Patta Script logo waist bag, a compact multi-compartment cross body bag, a classic backpack, and a large messenger backpack. All of the bags have been constructed using durable ripstop fabric with heavy duty suede accents and finished with YKK zipper hardware.
The pieces are slated to arrive on March 17 and you will find them in store and over at the Patta website .
Now get the lowdown on Brazil’s burgeoning streetwear community.
